DURING THE REACTION,

902
00:48:29,574 --> 00:48:30,867
BUT OTHERWISE
HE'S FEELING FINE.

903
00:48:30,991 --> 00:48:31,576
AND YOURSELF?

904
00:48:31,701 --> 00:48:33,703
VERY WELL. A FEW BRUISES
HERE AND THERE.

905
00:48:33,828 --> 00:48:34,412
OH.

906
00:48:34,537 --> 00:48:36,955
ANYTIME YOU'RE
READY, MR. SPOCK.

907
00:48:37,081 --> 00:48:40,334
I AM QUITE READY NOW,
DOCTOR.

908
00:48:40,459 --> 00:48:42,294
BECAUSE OF
YOUR VULCAN PHYSIQUE,

909
00:48:42,420 --> 00:48:45,130
I HAVE PREPARED
AN EXTREMELY POTENT
SHOT FOR YOU.

910
00:48:45,256 --> 00:48:46,883
