I THOUGHT YOU
MIGHT LIKE TO KNOW

911
00:48:47,007 --> 00:48:49,510
I'VE REMOVED
ALL THE BREAKABLES
FROM SICK BAY.

912
00:48:49,635 --> 00:48:52,221
THAT'S VERY CONSIDERATE
OF YOU, DOCTOR.

913
00:48:52,346 --> 00:48:53,598
I THOUGHT YOU'D
BE PLEASED TO HEAR THAT.

914
00:48:57,351 --> 00:48:59,061
WELL, GENTLEMEN,
ALL AND ALL,

915
00:48:59,186 --> 00:49:02,565
AN EXPERIENCE
WE'LL REMEMBER
IN OUR OLD AGE...

916
00:49:02,690 --> 00:49:07,486
WHICH WON'T BE
FOR SOME WHILE, I HOPE.

917
00:49:07,612 --> 00:49:08,571
TAKE OVER, MR. SULU.

918
00:49:08,696 --> 00:49:10,698
STEADY AS SHE GOES.

919
00:49:10,823 --> 00:49:12,909
STEADY AS SHE GOES,
CAPTAIN.

920
00:49:13,033 --> 00:49:14,201
I THOUGHT I SAID THAT.
